/* MCSAsub - collect MCS events into arrays.
 * aSub record fields:
 *  vala[]  Array 1
 *  valb[]  Array 2
 *  valc[]  Array 3
 *  vald[]  Array 4
 *  vale[]  Array 5
 *  valr[]  Array 6
 *  valg[]  Array 7
 *  valh    number of events
 *  a       number of scalers
 *  d       clear arrays
 *	e		clock rate counter1
 *
 * Tim Mooney
 */

